Outline

  1. What is the tidyverse?
  2. Useful functions to know

Data source

All flower phenology data is from the USA Phenology Network. In this workshop, we work with species that occur on Serrano, Cahuilla, Mojave, and Chemehuevi ancestral land, or Joshua Tree National Park.
